{"tid":2020513,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"持續進修基金一問","createTime":"2020-05-17T06:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T14:02:26.000Z","uid":122558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e3435304493e792f1229c0778508ced6be57b6","tid":2020513,"uid":122558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"持續進修基金為有志進修的成年人提供持續教育和培訓資助。符合資格的申請人於成功修畢持續進修基金可獲發還款項課程（基金課程）後一年內及年齡屆滿71歲前，可不限次數申領合共最多20,000港元的資助。首10,000港元資助的學員共付比率（即學員本身需負擔的費用的百分比）為課程費用的20%，而次10,000港元資助的學員共付比率則為課程費用的40%。<br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係一個course超過兩萬蚊都只係攞個course既20%再加40%錢？<br />\n<br />\n姐係一個1萬既course 既 拎2000加4000咁？"},{"pid":"18876197eb22ed2a9caee85e485ff8112fb62d6a","tid":2020513,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:48:13.000Z","msg":"問返科程主任<br />\n科科唔同"},{"pid":"697308da02fd0b9c37cc0bcf0439fc5c9fb481f1","tid":2020513,"uid":122558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"18876197eb22ed2a9caee85e485ff8112fb62d6a","tid":2020513,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:48:13.000Z","msg":"問返科程主任<br />\n科科唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"仲以為可以一科拎哂"},{"pid":"a6fa892a8fba58c7795d417e72e287d830a9974b","tid":2020513,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"697308da02fd0b9c37cc0bcf0439fc5c9fb481f1","tid":2020513,"uid":122558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"18876197eb22ed2a9caee85e485ff8112fb62d6a","tid":2020513,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:48:13.000Z","msg":"問返科程主任<br />\n科科唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"仲以為可以一科拎哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"你睇清楚20%係乜黎先"},{"pid":"c59e01d43fe51ddeea2dd412b28daa65f39bc4ee","tid":2020513,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"上 CEF 個網有 online calculator 幫你計"}]}